                    </div>
                    <div class="rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col justify-center" style="background-color: #44403C;">
                        <p class="text-[16px] font-bold" style="color: #FEF3C7;">猎户座</p>
                        <p class="text-[13px] mt-1" style="color: #A8A29E;">冬夜最壮丽的星座</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col justify-center" style="background-color: #44403C;">
                        <p class="text-[16px] font-bold" style="color: #FEF3C7;">银河</p>
                        <p class="text-[13px] mt-1" style="color: #A8A29E;">横跨天际的星之河流</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col justify-center" style="background-color: #44403C;">
                        <p class="text-[16px] font-bold" style="color: #FEF3C7;">流星</p>
                        <p class="text-[13px] mt-1" style="color: #A8A29E;">转瞬即逝的美丽</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 右栏 -->
            <div class="w-[380px] flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col gap-4">
                <div class="flex-1 rounded-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-center text-center" style="background-color: #78350F;">
                    <div class="text-[28px] mb-2" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">"</div>
                    <p class="text-[18px] leading-loose italic" style="color: #FEFCE8;">我们都是星尘做的，<br/>仰望星空时，<br/>也是星空在凝视我们。</p>
                    <p class="text-[13px] mt-3" style="color: #FDE68A;">— 卡尔·萨根</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg p-5" style="background-color: #292524;">
