                        <li class="text-[13px] flex items-start gap-2" style="color: #D6D3D1;"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #B45309;"></span>选择晴朗无月的夜晚</li>
                        <li class="text-[13px] flex items-start gap-2" style="color: #D6D3D1;"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #B45309;"></span>让眼睛适应黑暗20分钟</li>
